    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but thats what everyone says. \"it gets better\" or \"you just need help\". i've tried the help. i've tried everything. it's not just like a bad mood, it's like... the foundation is just gone. like if you try to fix a house where the ground is shifting constantly, it's just a waste of time. eventually you just have to accept that the house is gone. i think i'm just fundamentally unfixable.",
